import React from 'react'
import { Container , Nav , Navbar , NavDropdown, Image} from 'react-bootstrap'
import LogoBlack from "./LogoBlack";


const Menu = () => {

    const logoDataURL = `data:image/svg+xml;base64,${btoa(
        new XMLSerializer().serializeToString(<LogoBlack />)
    )}`;

    const styles = {
        width: '60px',
        height: '60px',
        backgroundSize: 'cover',
        backgroundPosition: 'center',
        backgroundRepeat: 'no-repeat',
        backgroundColor: 'blue',
        
    };
    return (
        <>
        <Navbar bg="light" className='shadow' expand="false" >
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Brand href="#home" style={styles}>
                        <Image src='LogoBlack'></Image>
                </Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#link">BI - Dashboard</Nav.Link>
                        <NavDropdown bg="dark"  title="FormulÃ¡rios de Atesto" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                            <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                        </NavDropdown>
                        <NavDropdown title="Matriz de Risco" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Form1</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Form2</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Something</NavDropdown.Item>
                        </NavDropdown>
                        <Nav.Link href="#link">Ajuda</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#link">Sair</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
        </>
    )
    }

export default Menu
